WEBVTT

00:05:29.514 --> 00:05:33.299
Not even schoolchildren
are more important than cars.

00:05:33.299 --> 00:05:35.540
In my city of BogotÃ¡,

00:05:35.540 --> 00:05:38.894
we fought a very difficult battle

00:05:38.894 --> 00:05:41.668
in order to take space from cars,

00:05:41.668 --> 00:05:44.564
which had been parking on sidewalks for decades,

00:05:44.564 --> 00:05:47.679
